Trainers

Ignatius looked over head and saw The Ark come into view.

"Looks like were here now. Time to drop down."

Igntous plunged downwards and landed beside Prebon. Prebon lifted her 
off the Eagle's wings and immediatly embraced her.

"Alright. Are we ready? Hammer and Ignatius will hold you so that I 
may cry to the Maximals. Remember, best performance ever."
